ecialising in defined product or market sectors and are committed to their clients relationship with the macquarie group within overall guidelines and a strong risk management framework the operating groups have substantial discretion in the way they manage their business activities great emphasis is placed on a clients relationship with macquarie as a whole four service groups provide the framework infrastructure and support that the operating groups require to manage their business these are the corporate operations financial management legal and governance and risk management groups   our support groups our businesses are supported by specialist global teams corporate operations group financial management group risk management group legal and governance leadership and corporate governance macquarie aims to deliver long term profitability and shareholder returns while managing risk and observing expected standards of corporate governance our leadership team has deep experience across the organisation while our board comprises a diverse range of respected business leaders corporate governance leadership risk management at macquarie environmental social  governance diversity and inclusion about macquarie what we stand for three principles guide our approach opportunity accountability and integrity find out more holey dollar our symbol the holey dollar is synonymous with a history of banking and innovation find out more history we opened the doors to our sydney office in  with three people now were a global business find out more careers  search  international sites select a country  australia  indonesia  south africa  austria  ireland  sweden  brazil  japan  switzerland  canada  korea  taiwan  china  malaysia  thailand  france  netherlands  united arab emirates  germany  new zealand  united kingdom  hong kong  philippines  united states  india  singapore about macquarie about macquarie group investor relations careers related sites contact site map macquarie careers